name: This might steal your face - "for da lot"
description: Decided to make another run of this. https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/62028 was the original variant that started with 13 and burned down to 1. This is what looks like to me as a stealie. For those who may not know, a stealie is a skull art associated with the grateful dead. I love their music, thought it looked cool.
